abstract: Tiger Woods has poor outing at Frys.com Open golf tournament after seven-week break, leaving him in danger of missing cut in two consecutive starts for first time in his career.
snippet: Tiger Woods went 13 holes between his two birdies in the Frys.com Open in San Martin, Calif., and had to work hard for a two-over 73.
